// Real rescue dogs imported from Stray Dogs Center UAE
// (straydogscenteruae.com/adult-dogs). Name, gender and (where stated) breed
// are parsed from each gallery entry's title; the bio, date of birth/age and
// health/temperament notes are taken from the entry's description. Ages are
// computed from the date of birth or stated age (relative to import date).
// The centre rarely labels a breed or size, so those default to "Ask shelter".
